'''4-氯吡啶'''是一种[[有机化合物|有机化合物]]，化学式为C<sub>5</sub>H<sub>4</sub>ClN，它是[[氯吡啶|氯吡啶]]的[[同分异构体|同分异构体]]之一。

==制备==
4-氯吡啶可由[[N-氧化吡啶|吡啶-''N''-氧化物]]和[[氯化亚砜|氯化亚砜]]反应得到。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Bobrański|first1=Boguslaw|last2=Kochańska|first2=Lidia|last3=Kowalewska|first3=Anna|title=Über die Einwirkung von Sulfurylchlorid auf Pyridinoxyd|journal=Berichte der deutschen chemischen Gesellschaft (A and B Series)|volume=71|issue=11|year=1938|pages=2385–2388|issn=03659488|doi=10.1002/cber.19380711126}}</ref>{{link-de|4-吡啶酮|4-Pyridon}}和[[五硫化二磷|五硫化二磷]]反应，得到4-巯基吡啶，再与[[氯气|氯气]]反应，得到4-氯吡啶。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=King|first1=Harold|last2=Ware|first2=Lancelot L.|title=186. 4–Thiopyridone and derived substances|journal=J. Chem. Soc.|volume=0|issue=0|year=1939|pages=873–877|issn=0368-1769|doi=10.1039/JR9390000873}}</ref>

4-氯吡啶-''N''-氧化物在[[二氯二氧化钼|二氯二氧化钼]]的催化下由[[氢气|氢气]]还原<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Reis|first1=Patrícia M.|last2=Royo|first2=Beatriz|title=Chemoselective hydrogenation of nitroarenes and deoxygenation of pyridine N-oxides with H2 catalyzed by MoO<sub>2</sub>Cl<sub>2</sub>|journal=Tetrahedron Letters|volume=50|issue=8|year=2009|pages=949–952|issn=00404039|doi=10.1016/j.tetlet.2008.12.038}}</ref>，或者直接用[[氯化锂|LiCl]]/[[硼氢化钠|NaBH<sub>4</sub>]]还原<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Ram|first1=S. Raja|last2=Chary|first2=K. Purushothama|last3=Iyengar|first3=D. S.|title=An Efficient and Chemoselective Deoxygenation of Hetero Cyclic N-Oxides Using Licl/nabh4|journal=Synthetic Communications|volume=30|issue=19|year=2000|pages=3511–3515|issn=0039-7911|doi=10.1080/00397910008087263}}</ref>，都可以得到4-氯吡啶。

==反应==
4-氯吡啶可以在[[甲醇钾|甲醇钾]]的存在下（[[:d:Q72444870|二(亚苄基丙酮)钯]]催化）脱氯，得到[[吡啶|吡啶]]。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Viciu|first1=Mihai S.|last2=Grasa|first2=Gabriela A.|last3=Nolan|first3=Steven P.|title=Catalytic Dehalogenation of Aryl Halides Mediated by a Palladium/Imidazolium Salt System|journal=Organometallics|volume=20|issue=16|year=2001|pages=3607–3612|issn=0276-7333|doi=10.1021/om010332s}}</ref>4-氯吡啶的氯也能被其它基团取代，如它和[[叠氮化钠|叠氮化钠]]反应可以得到[[:d:Q82287086|4-叠氮基吡啶]]。<ref>Livi, O.; Ferrarini, P. L.; Tonetti, I.; Smaldone, F.; Zefola, G. Synthesis and pharmacological screening of 1,​2,​3-​triazole derivatives of naphthalene, quinoline, pyridine. ''Farmaco, Edizione Scientifica'', 1979. 34 (3): 217-218. ISSN: 0430-0920.</ref>它和[[二氟化银|二氟化银]]反应，进一步被卤代，生成2-氟-4-氯吡啶。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Fier|first1=P. S.|last2=Hartwig|first2=J. F.|title=Selective C-H Fluorination of Pyridines and Diazines Inspired by a Classic Amination Reaction|journal=Science|volume=342|issue=6161|year=2013|pages=956–960|issn=0036-8075|doi=10.1126/science.1243759}}</ref>

4-氯吡啶可以发生[[乌尔曼反应|乌尔曼反应]]，生成[[4,4'-联吡啶|4,4'-联吡啶]]。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Puthiaraj|first1=Pillaiyar|last2=Ahn|first2=Wha-Seung|title=Ullmann coupling of aryl chlorides in water catalyzed by palladium nanoparticles supported on amine-grafted porous aromatic polymer|journal=Molecular Catalysis|volume=437|year=2017|pages=73–79|issn=24688231|doi=10.1016/j.mcat.2017.05.003}}</ref>在[[碳酸钾|碳酸钾]]存在下，它和吡啶-3-硼酸发生[[铃木偶联反应|铃木偶联反应]]，生成3,4'-联吡啶。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Fleckenstein|first1=Christoph A.|last2=Plenio|first2=Herbert|title=Highly Efficient Suzuki–Miyaura Coupling of Heterocyclic Substrates through Rational Reaction Design|journal=Chemistry - A European Journal|volume=14|issue=14|year=2008|pages=4267–4279|issn=09476539|doi=10.1002/chem.200701877}}</ref>
